sionals our ma team works closely with bmo’s sector specialists and other product professionals to provide clients with our best strategic advice   we can help you evaluate and if appropriate pursue emerging opportunities from a valueadded merger or acquisition to realigning your capital structure to maximizing shareholder value through a sale of assets or of the company as a whole in the us we specialize in providing handson ma advice to corporations financial sponsors and familyowned companies within the midcap space with the agility of an advisory boutique organization and the resources of a large diversified and well capitalized financial institution bmo capital markets can help your company reach its most ambitious goals   industry expertise   capabilities   extensive advisory experience in north american and international ma including mergers acquisitions divestitures joint ventures leveraged buyouts and takeover defenses expertise in restructuring recapitalizations and north american bankruptcy processes wellestablished client relationships across north american industry sectors strong track record in both contested bids and friendly transactions acquisition  divestiture focusing on the energy sector provides buyandsell side advisory fairness opinions and valuations view ad advisory publications   view current deals wellpositioned real estate brokerage group   bmo completes acquisition of ma advisory firm greene holcomb fisher contact info   advisory   canada     us       advisory  ad   canada     us     emea       capital raising     access to capital is critical to your companys business strategy whether youre looking to finance an acquisition or bolster liquidity we can open the door to global capital markets we have decades of experience raising capital for highgrade corporate and public issuers in canada and a growing volume of highyield issuances and private placements in the us our broad array of financing solutions ranges from traditional loans and commitments to complex structured financing   capabilities   access to hybrid corporate securities specialpurpose securities and derivative strategies unparalleled sales and trading capabilities public equity transactions on guaranteedbought deal basis in us ability to transact in various currencies at fixed or floating rates flexible stratified debt structures fixed income market coverage convertible securities corporate broking corporate lending loan syndications mezzanine debt private equity securitization   contact info   canada     us         global trade  banking your business crosses borders and so do we with offices in  locations around the world including  in north america we can help you seize profitable opportunities wherever they are global banking our bank coverage global team is bmo financial groups coordinating point for international banktobank relationships they provide client coverage and sales  marketing expertise in support of global treasury management investment banking market risk management global trade finance our relationship managers cover more than  international financial institutions in europe africa the middle east australasia and latin america see regulatory reporting requirements global trade finance our global trade finance team offers the full trade finance capabilities and service commitment you expect from a leading financial institution including documentary credits standby letters of credit and guarantees international collections approval to pay working capital solutions global banking contact info americas     asia     europemena     global trade finance contact info toronto canada     montreal canada     us     conferences   there are no current conferences for this industry     institutional investing     your business has ambitious goals bmo capital markets professional investment managers work closely with you to select investment options that help bring those goals within reach using a highly disciplined methodology we pro